snippet.title: Last Epoch Multiplayer Beta Patch 0 9 - Convergence Trailer
snippet.description:
The Last Epoch Multiplayer Beta 0.9 Patch launches March 9th, 2023! 

Fans of the incredible Last Epoch experience can expect a massive amount of updates, the beginning of the Multiplayer Beta, and a ton of new content. 

Be sure to join us on March 9th for Beta Patch 0.9 - Convergence! 

For more information, be sure to follow Last Epoch on: 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/LastEpoch
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lastepochgame
Discord: https://discord.gg/lastepoch

#LastEpoch
